{"tid":2329792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★遊戲內有「習近平小熊維尼」字眼，中國網友不滿，被逼下架","createTime":"2020-12-17T12:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T23:15:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3127933fd42f3c55e288b87321eade57a477daa7","tid":2329792,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:52:22.000Z","msg":"早前遊戲公司赤燭遊戲開發驚悚遊戲「還願」，但有玩家發現遊戲內有「習近平小熊維尼」字眼，隨即引起中國網友不滿，之後遊戲亦被下架。而遊戲公司赤燭遊戲近日就宣佈，「還願」遊戲會在 12 月 18 日於 GOG 遊戲平台重新上架，但是遊戲平台 GOG 就在宣佈後的幾小時，於 Twitter 宣佈，由於收到很多網民訊息，決定遊戲不會在 GOG 上架。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲平台 GOG 於 Twitter 宣佈，在今日稍早的時間，曾宣佈會重新上架遊戲「還願」，但是由於之後收到很多玩家的訊息，決定不會在其平台上架遊戲。據報導，GOG 是 CD Projekt 旗下的遊戲平台，有很多中國網友曾在 GOG 官方微博留言，會一同抵制遊戲《電馭叛客2077》（Cyberpubk2077）。有網友在 Twitter 留言，質疑 GOG 所稱的「很多玩家」是否指中國網民，另外亦有網友表示，對 GOG 的決定感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/17/gog-devotion/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F17%2Fgog-devotion%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28b9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=ef9676b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/17/gog-devotion/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"73da9c346300cb4cc2188ddc861c36c1c828b2e4","tid":2329792,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5856008317750d41f317210351815185ce0e03cd","tid":2329792,"uid":56550,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"班支那人訓著左？<br />\n還願出左咁撚耐都仲可以攞返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459155206e8ed28103438535c6e0310db2504b07","tid":2329792,"uid":194005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:27:32.000Z","msg":"五毛算唔算係玩家？"},{"pid":"9cc01ba99c88308d06d3d5749853f9e5a9e09d4b","tid":2329792,"uid":6497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"CD Projekt自己隻2077咪仲政治不正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩好跪"},{"pid":"a1431f46e11166f7d5ce007597772c7a188685a4","tid":2329792,"uid":183090,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9cc01ba99c88308d06d3d5749853f9e5a9e09d4b","tid":2329792,"uid":6497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"CD Projekt自己隻2077咪仲政治不正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩好跪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"呢隻係大作嚟（隻遊戲係好多 bug，有好多問題）<br />\n但支那人應該覺得真心想玩，所以當睇唔到，還願相反無 2077 咁popular，所以先吠得咁勁"},{"pid":"919eef1f8c26fbee52c95a97689a104eeb21bdb9","tid":2329792,"uid":242602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"[quote很多中國網友曾在 GOG 官方微博留言，會一同抵制遊戲《電馭叛客2077》][/quote]<br />\n<br />\n做咗先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋班友仔為咗玩隻驚無視台獨，改埋wiki掩耳盜鈴嘅嘢都做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0a2708799c48eab31682d9859f6eff21058ae2","tid":2329792,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"GOG系咩泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6718da4011ccfed43229d80e3bfe9d6fc76b8a0d","tid":2329792,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"老貓  今日猛料係Asus<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d883b129daed253a88f71b80bcf833bc030be9","tid":2329792,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T23:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jMXjC8XBlhk/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjMXjC8XBlhk%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=0a2dd850&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}